566f0c4f643661780f0042a2_51.original:
{{GM}}She shakes her head.{{/GM}}

Hell of a surprise... guess it doesn't matter now, though.

Reach into my pocket, $(l.name). Grab my PDA.

5671f1076266321824004dcf_5.original:
I'm not gonna lie, $(l.name)... I'm really hurting over here. I think I'm feeling the delayed aftereffects of that magical energy I soaked up back at the police station.

{{GM}}She swallows, her eyes darting. She looks nervous.{{/GM}}

Look, I'll do my best to see this through, but if anything should happen--

5546946b39393684190077c9_138.original:
{{GM}}Henry doesn't answer for a long time. When he finally speaks, his voice seems to come from very far away.{{/GM}}

It is, $(L.name)... it is.

It's time for me to go.

5546946b39393684190077c9_139.original:
You're right, $(L.name). She'll be there. Waiting for me.

{{GM}}He sighs heavily, like gust of sad wind.{{/GM}}

I'll stay this course just a little longer.

56097ecf643661801100391d_5.original:
{{GM}}Qiu cuts in, rubbing the bridge of her nose between her thumb and forefinger.{{/GM}}

